<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

{% include "./layout/head.ejs" %}

<body>
  {% include "./layout/navbar.ejs" %}
<div class="row my-3">
  <div class="col-lg-12">
    <h3>회원가입 시 주의사항</h3>
    <p>담당 층을 <strong class="text-primary">한 개만</strong> 적어주세요!
      <small class="text-muted">예) 19-20층장이라면, 숫자 '19' 만 입력</small>
    </p>
    <p>아이디는 <strong>영어 혹은 숫자</strong>의 조합으로 적어주세요.
      <small class="text-muted">(한글 불가)</small>
    </p>
    <p>닉네임은 영어, 한글, 숫자의 조합 안에서 가능합니다.</p>
    <p class="text-danger">비밀번호는 전부 암호화하여 DB에 저장되므로, 잃어버린 비밀번호는 찾아드릴 수 없습니다.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid">

  <div class="container-fluid my-4">

    <form id="join-form" action="/auth/join" method="post">
      <div class="form-group" style="max-width: 20rem; float: none; margin:0 auto;">
        <label class="form-label mt-4">Please sign in</label>
        <div class="form-floating mb-3">
          <input type="uid" class="form-control" id="uid" name="uid" placeholder="영어 or 영어+숫자">
          <label for="floatingInput">Id</label>
        </div>
        <div class="form-floating mb-3">
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="nick" name="nick" placeholder="한글도 ok">
          <label for="floatingPassword">닉네임</label>
        </div>
        <div class="form-floating mb-3">
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="floor" name="floor" placeholder="반드시 담당 층 1개만!">
          <label for="floatingPassword">담당 층</label>
        </div>
        <div class="form-floating mb-3">
          <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" name="password" placeholder="분실된 비밀번호는 못 찾아드립니다">
          <label for="floatingPassword">Password</label>
        </div>
        <div class="my-3" style="float: none; margin:0 auto;">
          <button id="login" type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">회원가입</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </form>


  </div>

</div>
    {% include "./layout/footer.ejs" %}
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
  <script src="//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="main.js"></script>
  <script>
    window.onload = () => {
      if (new URL(location.href).searchParams.get('error')) {
        alert('이미 존재하는 아이디입니다.');
      }
    };
  </script>
  {% block script %}
  {% endblock %}
</body>

</html>